      "content": "the block thing is a bit confusing with the way you're explaining it, actually. the \"running out of space\" part doesn't really make sense mathematically. can we just drop the party metaphors and the \"lone wolf\" stuff? it's making it harder to teach. can you just give me a direct, professional explanation of the divisibility rule for primes? something clean and standard for a classroom setting.",
